I think I should become a good person.


From now on,I will not murder cats.

Or squirrels.

But I think there are a few people I really have to kill.

Those people make me a bad person. That is an ever growing list. This is the biggest problem with the world. too many idiots running around thinking they are right. Like me.


That is true. I am right. But, I am not an idiot and I am not really running around. I am just sitting down being right. Complicated? Complex?
